&lt;li&gt;You will work with the Databricks technical team, Project Manager, Architect and Customer team to ensure the technical components of the engagement are delivered to meet customer&#39;s needs.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work with Engineering and Databricks Customer Support to provide product and implementation feedback and to guide rapid resolution for engagement specific product and support issues.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
